{"tid":1562874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月9號之前 希望大家盡量唔好搞魚蛋義士","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:14:52.000Z","uid":27670,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a75c460a0cd4ba8565d44303257dfc76374d081e","tid":1562874,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:48:25.000Z","msg":"留意到有post想去監獄附近唱歌俾天琦聽<br />\n我明白大家都好想用行動支持佢<br />\n但係 當政府仲係用緊打大台既手法處理抗爭既時候<br />\n好容易變成槍打出頭鳥 令到佢地得唔到公平既裁決<br />\n雖然我唔敢講我地唔做呢件事就一定可以令佢地出到黎<br />\n但係忽然咁做好容易將政府焦點shift去佢地度<br />\n尤其是時代革命既口號係出自天琦<br />\n仲有唔夠一個月 大家忍一忍好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好希望10月9號係可以大家一齊用歌聲迎接佢地出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199be3902d53441e8094c5aea9add1ede9503085","tid":1562874,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:49:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"aa31439bb026af477b4e5f94e7dd7668b604b105","tid":1562874,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:49:32.0